<h2 style="font-size: 22px;">Cape Fear Community College</h2>
<strong>Wilmington, NC</strong>

<div class="infolines">
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers credit for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-green">Yes</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers placement into higher-level courses for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-green">Yes</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
</div>


<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Cape Fear Community College may award credit for Advanced Placement exams taken at the high school level. The student is directed to contact his/her high school counselor for more information on the examinations. Test scores received at our institution are evaluated by the counselors for credit.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://cfcc.edu/cat/cat1213/Catalog2012-2013.pdf" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

